folders.name: ecust-jwc
folders.description:
# Ecust jwc module.

> Created by Fisher on 2016-09-22 at 21:24.

---


## Decleration of objects.

---

define <jwc-news-object>

- path: {String}
  - News path in jwc-web-site.
- name: {String}
  - News name.
- date: {String}
  - News published date.
- tag: {Number}
  - News tag.
- md5: {String}
  - md5(name+path+date).
- attachments: [{{jwc-news-attachment-object}}]

---

define <jwc-news-attachment-object>

- path: {String}
  - Attachment path in jwc-web-site.
- name: {String}
  - Attachment name.
- format: {String}
  - Attachment format.
- size: {Number} *Only when attachment is a file.*
  - Attachment size.
- md5: {String} *Only when attachment is a file.*
  - md5(attachment-content).
